description: Kanuka Clancy is a police officer on loan from the New York Police Department. She`s a Japanese-American born in Oahu, Hawaii. A competent officer who is skilled at jobs as varied as bomb disposal and anti-terrorism, she does everything by the book and is often disgusted by the tactics used by the SV2, where she acts as http://anidb.net/ch11748 [Oota]`s backup. Among the SV2, there is a rumour that the NYPD sent her to them because she was a problem officer.
name: Kanuka Clancy
